  "title": "Manufacturing Technician x20 (Semiconductor / ASAP / EAST)",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Our client, a Global MNC in the Semiconductor industry</li><li><strong>Mass hiring for Manufacturing Technicians x 30</strong></li><li>5 days work shift, 8.5 hours</li><li>Nearest MRT: Upper Changi</li><li>Company Transport provided</li></ul><p><strong>The Talent</strong></p><ul><li>NITEC or Higher NITEC or Diploma in Electrical, Electronics, Mechanical, Mechatronic, Microelectronics or any Engineering related studies</li><li>Experience in Assembly, Build, Test, Preventive Maintenance</li><li>Candidates with or without experience are welcome to apply!</li></ul><p><strong>The Job</strong></p><ul><li>Working in the Production Centre and Cleanroom environment</li><li>Responsible for maintenance and troubleshooting of the Tools and Equipment</li><li>Handling testing and assembled equipment</li><li>In-charge of the set-up and calibration of the equipment/machine/tool</li><li>Understanding electrical/mechanical diagrams and drawings</li><li>Perform QA/QC checks duties</li></ul><p><strong>Next Step</strong></p><ul><li>Simply click on 'Apply here' to drop your resume or email to <strong>edmond.lee@adecco.com</strong></li><li>All shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</li></ul><p><br />Edmond Lee</p><p>Direct Line: 8206 8857</p><p>EA License No: 91C2918</p><p>Personnel Registration Number: R23114813</p>",
